dc:description: Fragment of woven wool fabric with brown warp, a very deteriorated brown weft band and 12.5 cm of a green/blue weft band with remnants of linen weft wrapping and slit tapestry.  There is a row of stitching near one end of the green/blue band.  There are remnants of red countered weft-twining in the brown weft band.  The twining loops pass over two warps each.
